AT1 -[#red,dashed]up--> A1 : threatens
AT2 -[#red,dashed]up--> A1 : threatens
AT3 -[#red,dashed]up--> A1 : threatens
AT4 -[#red,dashed]up--> A1 : threatens

' === Mitigates relationships (unchanged - they were already correct) ===
A3 -[#green,dashed]-> AT1 : mitigates
A3 -[#green,dashed]-> AT2 : mitigates
